@flouthoc  thank you for looking into (and fixing) this.

I've built buildah from 4093 and confirmed it now works as intended.

fwiw I also tried just running `export XDG_RUNTIME_DIR=/run/user/$UID` after sudo and that also worked (as this directory already exists because I am running ghrunner via systemd).  Maybe useful to anyone as a workaround
